Police Minister Bheki Cele is also expected to address members of the security cluster about the deployment plans in and around Cape Town to ensure the safety and security of the President during this year's SONA.   

For the first time since 1994 the SONA will be delivered at the iconic Cape Town City Hall where former late President Nelson Mandela made his first speech after his release from prison on February the tenth 1990.  
  
--SABC--